uppercase: HALF A LEAGUE ONWARD,
uppercase: ALL IN THE VALLEY OF DEATH
uppercase: RODE THE SIX HUNDRED.
uppercase: 2.
uppercase: "FORWARD, THE LIGHT BRIGADE!
uppercase: "CHARGE FOR THE GUNS!" HE SAID:
uppercase: INTO THE VALLEY OF DEATH
uppercase: RODE THE SIX HUNDRED.
uppercase: "FORWARD, THE LIGHT BRIGADE!"
uppercase: WAS THERE A MAN DISMAY'D?
uppercase: NOT THO' THE SOLDIER KNEW
uppercase: SOMEONE HAD BLUNDER'D:
uppercase: THEIRS NOT TO MAKE REPLY,
uppercase: THEIRS NOT TO REASON WHY,
uppercase: THEIRS BUT TO DO AND DIE:
uppercase: INTO THE VALLEY OF DEATH
uppercase: RODE THE SIX HUNDRED.
uppercase: 3.
uppercase: CANNON TO RIGHT OF THEM,
uppercase: CANNON TO LEFT OF THEM,
uppercase: CANNON IN FRONT OF THEM
uppercase: VOLLEY'D AND THUNDER'D;
uppercase: STORM'D AT WITH SHOT AND SHELL,
uppercase: BOLDLY THEY RODE AND WELL,
uppercase: INTO THE JAWS OF DEATH,
uppercase: INTO THE MOUTH OF HELL
uppercase: RODE THE SIX HUNDRED.
uppercase: 4.
uppercase: FLASH'D ALL THEIR SABRES BARE,
uppercase: FLASH'D AS THEY TURN'D IN AIR,
uppercase: SABRING THE GUNNERS THERE,
uppercase: CHARGING AN ARMY, WHILE
uppercase: ALL THE WORLD WONDER'D:
uppercase: PLUNGED IN THE BATTERY-SMOKE
uppercase: RIGHT THRO' THE LINE THEY BROKE;
uppercase: COSSACK AND RUSSIAN
uppercase: REEL'D FROM THE SABRE STROKE
uppercase: SHATTER'D AND SUNDER'D.
uppercase: THEN THEY RODE BACK, BUT NOT
uppercase: NOT THE SIX HUNDRED.
uppercase: 5.
uppercase: CANNON TO RIGHT OF THEM,
uppercase: CANNON TO LEFT OF THEM,
uppercase: CANNON BEHIND THEM
uppercase: VOLLEY'D AND THUNDER'D;
uppercase: STORM'D AT WITH SHOT AND SHELL,
uppercase: WHILE HORSE AND HERO FELL,
uppercase: THEY THAT HAD FOUGHT SO WELL
uppercase: CAME THRO' THE JAWS OF DEATH
uppercase: BACK FROM THE MOUTH OF HELL,
uppercase: ALL THAT WAS LEFT OF THEM,
uppercase: LEFT OF SIX HUNDRED.
uppercase: 6.
uppercase: WHEN CAN THEIR GLORY FADE?
uppercase: O THE WILD CHARGE THEY MADE!
uppercase: ALL THE WORLD WONDERED.
uppercase: HONOR THE CHARGE THEY MADE,
uppercase: HONOR THE LIGHT BRIGADE,
uppercase: NOBLE SIX HUNDRED.
